OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,7,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Another hot ay inland,
OL,9,Fthough a little cooler along some
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMost seeing clear spells
OL,13,Fovernight with intermittent areas of
OL,14,Fcloud. Winds dropping out and staying
OL,15,Fmild overnight, but more comfortable
OL,16,Fthan recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
